<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2020-03-17</DATELINE><TITLE>Funding gap for locust crisis</TITLE><BODY>East Africa is experiencing the worst desert locust outbreak in decades. Climate events have facilitated breeding of the swarming pest across the region, and with a surge in the locust population expected in coming weeks urgent action is needed to avert a humanitarian crisis.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>